{"tid":858822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭質疑 收回粉嶺高爾夫球場 建屋: 不能 「短期見效」","createTime":"2018-10-12T05:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T08:03:05.000Z","uid":53060,"like":4,"dislike":180,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"1776251e3bff2aeec1990d44924ab91d6eeb76c9","tid":858822,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:29:40.000Z","msg":"2018-10-12<br />\n<br />\n香港文匯報訊（記者 鄭治祖）不少人提出，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>粉嶺高爾夫球場可否用作短期建屋</strong></span>，林鄭月娥昨日坦言，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>即使能動用有關土地，亦不能短期見效</strong></span>，因為還要解決交通、搬祖墳和古樹的問題，「所以，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>有時候大家看似很快的選項其實不會很快。</strong></span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，收回粉嶺高爾夫球場建屋的建議，是土地供應專責小組的選項之一，亦是相對富爭議性的選項，待專責小組在年底交報告時再看情況如何。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2018/10/12/HK1810120005.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2FHK1810120005.htm&d=WS%2FYp3ECWde12OldG2sREYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=3ba9e24d\" target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2018/10/12/HK1810120005.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a34e802da97d9fade5bf8acd7236ea1c2fc51d4e","tid":858822,"uid":53060,"like":4,"dislike":44,"score":-40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsdb.memehk.com/img/post/20051_Coverphotosize.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsdb.memehk.com%2Fimg%2Fpost%2F20051_Coverphotosize.jpg&h=0ea9fe0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a095ff1a575c480d338cfb650f9bcd7552d615e","tid":858822,"uid":114097,"like":328,"dislike":2,"score":326,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/12/133110_d101bab8bac64e36d86ee70ba73a9c9c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2F133110_d101bab8bac64e36d86ee70ba73a9c9c.png&h=8fc981c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22a47c0d18e3474111